    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to the pot with a generous squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong>, a<strong> </strong>knob of<strong> butter </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth, then season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>lemon mash</strong></p>",
